headline: Barclays Reviews Fastenal (FAST) as Lower Pricing Weighs on Results
summary: Fastenal Company (NASDAQ:FAST) is included among the Dividend Growth Stocks: 25 Aristocrats. On January 21, Barclays lowered its price target on Fastenal Company (NASDAQ:FAST) to $43 from $44 and kept an Equal Weight rating following the company’s fourth-quarter results.
